in: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190228183316O5mMSXobF4H8IWJt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499634\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190228183316mUyRsSkCw8neFKjJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/runway/fall-ready-to-wear-2019/paris/lemaire-3/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lemaire 2019 秋冬：</a></strong></p><p>秀场选在了巴黎杜佩雷高等应用艺术学院（École Duperré art school）。大量看上去似乎被拉长的单色调廓形是受超现实主义艺术家 Paul Delvaux 影响，肩部线条也扮演了很大作用。Christophe Lemaire&nbsp;说他希望这个系列能看上去亲切一点，观众离 T 台坐得很近，阳光洒进来，给模特的面容和服装带来一种温柔平和的质感，也能更充分体现面料本身的特点。</p><p><em>WWD</em> 评价这个系列具有恰如其分的“艺术中产氛围”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190228183447Y3d5X2npZkHx6uKS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190228183442l0xgL5HUnmPOhqD4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190228183442L4FUADXYsEmufOPy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190228183442Gw9MtCSZzPNokxba.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902281834436LpeY4tx8uoROZyr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190228183443Ro8FDgT6MZJ3OrUA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190228183443FORoDiIaLBAvf9lb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902281834446og2eiI7LM4SE85h.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902281834448n4RCDr1ecv9BE75.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732